					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Also, as a developer, it's a good idea to configure your emulators to display all 240 scanlines (some emulators hide the top and bottom 8 scanlines by default, because some games have glitches in those areas and real TVs tend to hide some of those scanlines too), so you can see the whole picture your code is producing and detect problems that maybe you wouldn't notice otherwise.</div>

