				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Yeah, a Y scroll of 248 or 232 will result in the same picture from scanline 8 onwards, but scanlines 0-7 will be different: 248 will show garbage (attribute table data interpreted as name table data), 232 will show the bottom row of the name table.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

