						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">sailense wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">Right now I'm resetting scoll values in all my subroutines where I write to $2006. Is that the best way to go? And when is the best time to read from controller? Every NMI or during the main loop?</div><br />I can think of theoretical situations where someone <em>might</em> want to read and use input in the NMI, but in general there's no reason to read the controller more often than you do something with those read values, so probably I'd suggest main loop.</div>

